v1.0.2: Code review fixes - 17 improvements

- ps -A fallback for older ROMs (customize.sh)
- st_name bounds check in GOT patcher
- Return value check on apply_property_hooks
- Exact package matching (no substring false positives)
- System app blacklist (prevent accidental system hook)
- Target list write deduplication (no redundant I/O)
- Removed dead code (g_env, SOCKET_PATH)
- Native Android logging (logcat tag GhostBoot)
- mprotect failure logging with errno
- service.sh retry loop (5 attempts)
- customize.sh getprop guards for set -eu safety
- Removed redundant tmpfs size=0 fallback
- config.cpp list() lifetime documented
- ProGuard keep rules for DataStore + Compose
- module.prop bumped to v1.0.2
- APK versionCode bumped to 102
- Android.mk now links -llog
